doc202,orphaned land the storm still rages insi albüm ad mabool the lightning flashes tension s high bringing light to darkened skies lik jonah in the belly of the beast insi the ark the sound desist and so the ark swept upon the rising water forty days and forty nights ther came a mighty flood upon the land where once were green pastures teeming with lif now were oceans deeper than any abyss out of depths of sorrow i cry before the i li if this world shall inherit the mild hear your orphaned child lord pray to save thy child the storm still rages insi lord gui them unto dry land amen,"['orphaned', 'land', 'the', 'storm', 'still', 'rages', 'insi', 'albüm', 'ad', 'mabool', 'the', 'lightning', 'flashes', 'tension', 's', 'high', 'bringing', 'light', 'to', 'darkened', 'skies', 'lik', 'jonah', 'in', 'the', 'belly', 'of', 'the', 'beast', 'insi', 'the', 'ark', 'the', 'sound', 'desist', 'and', 'so', 'the', 'ark', 'swept', 'upon', 'the', 'rising', 'water', 'forty', 'days', 'and', 'forty', 'nights', 'ther', 'came', 'a', 'mighty', 'flood', 'upon', 'the', 'land', 'where', 'once', 'were', 'green', 'pastures', 'teeming', 'with', 'lif', 'now', 'were', 'oceans', 'deeper', 'than', 'any', 'abyss', 'out', 'of', 'depths', 'of', 'sorrow', 'i', 'cry', 'before', 'the', 'i', 'li', 'if', 'this', 'world', 'shall', 'inherit', 'the', 'mild', 'hear', 'your', 'orphaned', 'child', 'lord', 'pray', 'to', 'save', 'thy', 'child', 'the', 'storm', 'still', 'rages', 'insi', 'lord', 'gui', 'them', 'unto', 'dry', 'land', 'amen']"
