doc232,orson welles i know what it is to be young albüm ad i know what it is to be young when we are young age has no meaning i never gave it a second thought until one day along came this old man and this is what he said to me yes this is what he said to me i know what it is to be young but yo yo don t know what it is to be old someday yo ll be saying the same thing tim takes away so the story is told i have so many questions for the wise man i met couldn t find all the answers no one has theirs as yet ther ll be days to remember full of laughter and tears after summer comes winter so go the years so my friend let s make music together i ll play the old while yo sing me the new in tim when your young days are over ther ll be someone sharing their tim with yo,"['orson', 'welles', 'i', 'know', 'what', 'it', 'is', 'to', 'be', 'young', 'albüm', 'ad', 'i', 'know', 'what', 'it', 'is', 'to', 'be', 'young', 'when', 'we', 'are', 'young', 'age', 'has', 'no', 'meaning', 'i', 'never', 'gave', 'it', 'a', 'second', 'thought', 'until', 'one', 'day', 'along', 'came', 'this', 'old', 'man', 'and', 'this', 'is', 'what', 'he', 'said', 'to', 'me', 'yes', 'this', 'is', 'what', 'he', 'said', 'to', 'me', 'i', 'know', 'what', 'it', 'is', 'to', 'be', 'young', 'but', 'yo', 'yo', 'don', 't', 'know', 'what', 'it', 'is', 'to', 'be', 'old', 'someday', 'yo', 'll', 'be', 'saying', 'the', 'same', 'thing', 'tim', 'takes', 'away', 'so', 'the', 'story', 'is', 'told', 'i', 'have', 'so', 'many', 'questions', 'for', 'the', 'wise', 'man', 'i', 'met', 'couldn', 't', 'find', 'all', 'the', 'answers', 'no', 'one', 'has', 'theirs', 'as', 'yet', 'ther', 'll', 'be', 'days', 'to', 'remember', 'full', 'of', 'laughter', 'and', 'tears', 'after', 'summer', 'comes', 'winter', 'so', 'go', 'the', 'years', 'so', 'my', 'friend', 'let', 's', 'make', 'music', 'together', 'i', 'll', 'play', 'the', 'old', 'while', 'yo', 'sing', 'me', 'the', 'new', 'in', 'tim', 'when', 'your', 'young', 'days', 'are', 'over', 'ther', 'll', 'be'