doc452,orange blue the lowest point on earth albüm ad songs of liberty at the deepest ground under the water lies the sin village of unanswered dreams the deceased estate of our fathers when my work is done it ll be my own it s only the water it s always the water that ll take yo in when your hope is broken that ll be your home that is your unspoken friend we re on the lowest point on earth hope for the highest grace of birth the world is drownded and rearranged we will never be the same agai we re on the lowest point on earth hope for the highest grace of birth how i wish that the raging sea will forgiv us to eternity we ll learn to love the whales to swim with the dolphins we might fall asleep find to endless peace when all the continents break up and set the tortured souls of its victims fre and worlds overfrozing madness is consigned to the sea it ll be the water it s always the water that ll be our home for centuries that ll be my downfall and my victory,"['orange', 'blue', 'the', 'lowest', 'point', 'on', 'earth', 'albüm', 'ad', 'songs', 'of', 'liberty', 'at', 'the', 'deepest', 'ground', 'under', 'the', 'water', 'lies', 'the', 'sin', 'village', 'of', 'unanswered', 'dreams', 'the', 'deceased', 'estate', 'of', 'our', 'fathers', 'when', 'my', 'work', 'is', 'done', 'it', 'll', 'be', 'my', 'own', 'it', 's', 'only', 'the', 'water', 'it', 's', 'always', 'the', 'water', 'that', 'll', 'take', 'yo', 'in', 'when', 'your', 'hope', 'is', 'broken', 'that', 'll', 'be', 'your', 'home', 'that', 'is', 'your', 'unspoken', 'friend', 'we', 're', 'on', 'the', 'lowest', 'point', 'on', 'earth', 'hope', 'for', 'the', 'highest', 'grace', 'of', 'birth', 'the', 'world', 'is', 'drownded', 'and', 'rearranged', 'we', 'will', 'never', 'be', 'the', 'same', 'agai', 'we', 're', 'on', 'the', 'lowest', 'point', 'on', 'earth', 'hope', 'for', 'the', 'highest', 'grace', 'of', 'birth', 'how', 'i', 'wish', 'that', 'the', 'raging', 'sea', 'will', 'forgiv', 'us', 'to', 'eternity', 'we', 'll', 'learn', 't