doc548,orange blue in love with a dream albüm ad in love with a dream the tim is bleeding into eternity yo can t make a long kiss when yo don t breathe and tim is against me but my mind can t leave and if yo refuse to be in touch with me oh please please let me be in love with my dream and i dreamt of flowers seaching for bees and sometimes my whiskey was drinking me i guess that yo heard my heartbeat through the crowd telling yo i ll be ther as long as yo care if yo doubt let yourself be in love with my dream and each dusk the moon is eating the sun and each dawn i wonder where my dreams have gone i wish i could be in love with reality i guess that yo heard my heartbeat through the crowd telling yo i ll be ther as long as yo care if yo doubt let yourself be in love with my dream i wish i could be in love with reality,"['orange', 'blue', 'in', 'love', 'with', 'a', 'dream', 'albüm', 'ad', 'in', 'love', 'with', 'a', 'dream', 'the', 'tim', 'is', 'bleeding', 'into', 'eternity', 'yo', 'can', 't', 'make', 'a', 'long', 'kiss', 'when', 'yo', 'don', 't', 'breathe', 'and', 'tim', 'is', 'against', 'me', 'but', 'my', 'mind', 'can', 't', 'leave', 'and', 'if', 'yo', 'refuse', 'to', 'be', 'in', 'touch', 'with', 'me', 'oh', 'please', 'please', 'let', 'me', 'be', 'in', 'love', 'with', 'my', 'dream', 'and', 'i', 'dreamt', 'of', 'flowers', 'seaching', 'for', 'bees', 'and', 'sometimes', 'my', 'whiskey', 'was', 'drinking', 'me', 'i', 'guess', 'that', 'yo', 'heard', 'my', 'heartbeat', 'through', 'the', 'crowd', 'telling', 'yo', 'i', 'll', 'be', 'ther', 'as', 'long', 'as', 'yo', 'care', 'if', 'yo', 'doubt', 'let', 'yourself', 'be', 'in', 'love', 'with', 'my', 'dream', 'and', 'each', 'dusk', 'the', 'moon', 'is', 'eating', 'the', 'sun', 'and', 'each', 'dawn', 'i', 'wonder', 'where', 'my', 'dreams', 'have', 'gone', 'i', 'wish', 'i', 'could', 'be', 'in', 'love', 'with', 'reality', 'i', 'guess', 'that', 'yo', 'heard', 'my', 'heartbeat', 'through', 'the', 'crowd', 'telling', 'yo', 'i', 'll', 'b