doc549,opeth white cluster albüm ad still lif still it came passing by the pieces weaved together rose the sun and fooled me with another day the knocking message called for my lif sealed the spell of my scrawny body soil to skin my next of kin damp air grasped stole the words and greeted me with a hiss this is forgiveness so i know once i repent i seal the lid i slither for yo and i m dying i find trust in hate they wear white for me seemingly jaded and lost i forge myself into your dreams and her i am your lif hangman clutching at his tools i will come for yo the noose is tied murmur through the crowd plunging into anywhere but her cloak captured sighs of relief as the primal touch brought me back and the last sight i did se is still her beckoning right behind me,"['opeth', 'white', 'cluster', 'albüm', 'ad', 'still', 'lif', 'still', 'it', 'came', 'passing', 'by', 'the', 'pieces', 'weaved', 'together', 'rose', 'the', 'sun', 'and', 'fooled', 'me', 'with', 'another', 'day', 'the', 'knocking', 'message', 'called', 'for', 'my', 'lif', 'sealed', 'the', 'spell', 'of', 'my', 'scrawny', 'body', 'soil', 'to', 'skin', 'my', 'next', 'of', 'kin', 'damp', 'air', 'grasped', 'stole', 'the', 'words', 'and', 'greeted', 'me', 'with', 'a', 'hiss', 'this', 'is', 'forgiveness', 'so', 'i', 'know', 'once', 'i', 'repent', 'i', 'seal', 'the', 'lid', 'i', 'slither', 'for', 'yo', 'and', 'i', 'm', 'dying', 'i', 'find', 'trust', 'in', 'hate', 'they', 'wear', 'white', 'for', 'me', 'seemingly', 'jaded', 'and', 'lost', 'i', 'forge', 'myself', 'into', 'your', 'dreams', 'and', 'her', 'i', 'am', 'your', 'lif', 'hangman', 'clutching', 'at', 'his', 'tools', 'i', 'will', 'come', 'for', 'yo', 'the', 'noose', 'is', 'tied', 'murmur', 'through', 'the', 'crowd', 'plunging', 'into', 'anywhere', 'but', 'her', 'cloak', 'captured', 'sighs', 'of', 'relief', 'as', 'the', 'primal', 'touch', 'brought', 'me', 'back', 'and', 'the', 'last', 'sight', 'i', 'did', 'se', 'is', 'still', 'her', 'beckoning', 'right', 'behind